							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Written by </span><a href='https://plus.google.com/u/0/114162951489960418846?rel=author'>John-Paul Briones</a></div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Views:</span> <span name='page_views' id='page_views'>37,727</span></div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;' title='Originally published: Sep 1, 2011'><span style='color:#606060;'>Published:</span> Apr 21, 2016</div>
